                  Proceed to Checkout
                </a>
              </div>

              <div class="mt-6 text-center text-sm text-muted-foreground">
                <p>
                  or
                  <a
                    href="/en/filters"
                    class="font-medium text-primary hover:text-primary/90"
                  >
                    Continue Shopping
